---
import "../styles/global.css"
import Header from "../components/Header.astro"
import Field from "../components/Field.astro"
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>About</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header/>
    <section>
      <h1>ABOUT ME</h1>
      <p>
        My name is <mark>Joseph G. Pinon</mark>. I grew up in <mark>Oakland, CA</mark>. 
        I enjoy exploring the fields of computer science, data analysis, thermodynamics, computational fluid dynamics and game development. I recieved my Bachelors and Masters of Science in Mechanical Engineering from <mark>Carnegie Mellon University</mark>. Currently I am working as an Air Battle Manager in the United States Air Force.
      </p>
      <h2>MY PURPOSE</h2>
      <article>
        <div class = "card">
          <h3>I</h3>
          Inspire others through my work and experiences.
        </div>
        <div class = "card">
          <h3>II</h3>
          Hold myself accountable to studying demanding topics
        </div>
        <div class = "card">
          <h3>III</h3>
          Propose unique solutions to challenging problems
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
article{
  display: flex;
}

.card {
  margin-right: 1rem;
  padding: 1rem;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
}

.card > p {
  text-align: center;
}

section{
  width: 75ch;
  margin-left: 20%;
  margin-top: 5rem;
  animation-name: fadein;
  animation-duration: 1s;
}
h1{
  font-size: 5rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
h2{
  margin-top: 3rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  font-size: 3rem;
}
h3{
  color: var(--set0);
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

p {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  text-align: left;
  text-wrap: wrap;
}
mark{
  color: var(--set0);
  background-color: transparent;
}

@keyframes fadein{
from{
  opacity: 0;
  translate: 25% 0%;
}
</style>
